docs.lead_paragraph: LONDON, May 23. -- What strikes one most about the great cumulative pageant at Moscow is the novel effect it is producing on the imagination of outside nations. No one seems before to have realized what a colossal thing Russia really is, or what prodigious results must follow when she begins to move about.
